### 返回用户成绩
``` json
{
    "msgID": "生成UUID",
    "msgType": "C-1",
    "msgData":{
         "isSuccess": true,
        "curData" :{
            "score" : 150,
        },
        "errorInfo": {}
    },
    "msgDesc": "发送给用户的成绩"
}
```

### 将用户成绩返回给对手
``` json
{
    "msgID": "生成UUID",
    "msgType": "C-2",
    "msgData":{
        "isSuccess": true,
        "curData" :{
            "score" : 150,
            "answer" : "A"
        },
        "errorInfo": {}
    },
    "msgDesc": "发送给对手的成绩"
}
```

